Doug Alleavitch



Mr. Doug Alleavitch is Vice President-Quality at Nevro Corp. Mr. Alleavitch was previously employed as Vice President-Manufacturing by AngioScore, Inc. He received his undergraduate degree from Cornell University, a graduate degree from the University of Illinois, a graduate degree from Illinois Institute of Technology and an MBA from the University of Illinois.



